{"id": 2248, "genre": 1001, "title": "收快递，你都有过哪些糟心经历?", "description": "和快递员、快递柜、门卫，以及你家门口消防柜的恩恩怨怨。", "record_count": 2473, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180328133619E8KUrPnVLaHR51AY.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-29T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 273410, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈，都是快递柜的锅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056584}, {"id": 273412, "content": "快递被速递易绑架", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217977}, {"id": 273413, "content": "不是送上门送上门吗？后来就成了他等着我我去取，我是南门，他在北门，哪家快递也一样，就好象商量好的一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297100}, {"id": 273414, "content": "快递信息：您的快递已经被 门口垫子 签收", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073792}, {"id": 273416, "content": "只有邮政不送快递", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272697}, {"id": 273928, "content": "千万不要用中国邮政！！不然包你寄啥丢啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069267}, {"id": 273418, "content": "寄快递的算吗？寄回家物种日历被收件员问：为什么要寄这种东西？我一个白眼心说：关你什么事！我不寄你有生意吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 273420, "content": "大纸箱被强塞快递柜，取件打不开柜门。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623263}, {"id": 273421, "content": "学校保安亭不允许代收，所以来不及拿的快递直接被丢在一边", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298780}, {"id": 273422, "content": "门卫大爷是另一个小区新转来的，老是搞忘这是这个小区，“我们这是xx小区呀，你送错了吧……”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214537}, {"id": 273168, "content": "为了不在家能收快递，隔三差五和门卫打招呼送东西搞好关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 273169, "content": "快递柜24小时没取件就得强制关注公众号，否则取不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 273170, "content": "自从有了快递柜，就算家里有人也不送货上门了，有时真是快递界的消费降级", "image": null, "praise_count": 443, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 273171, "content": "每次拆完快递都要把快递单毁尸灭迹，担心个人信息泄露", "image": null, "praise_count": 476, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 273427, "content": "默认送到小区旁边小烟酒店，付一块钱才能签收", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419664}, {"id": 273683, "content": "重要紧急但不贵重的东西，送错地址了，联系谁都找不回来，只能重新买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300711}, {"id": 273428, "content": "特别特别的慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268716}, {"id": 277269, "content": "不在家，快递小哥把快递交给邻居管理", "image": "img/option/option/20180422212224twPjGYBFMHEf2Sbg.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275677}, {"id": 273430, "content": "目前遇到的快递小哥都还蛮好 呼呼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257995}, {"id": 273431, "content": "喂，你是什么通？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299130}, {"id": 273433, "content": "放快递柜也不说快递到了，等自己发现了，超时了，要交钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190068}, {"id": 273434, "content": "邮政快递已经堵死我的心了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 273435, "content": "死活不拿上来。你特么是顺丰好嘛？我多交了钱了好嘛？！！送货到家懂不？！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244428}, {"id": 273437, "content": "邮政快递了 说都不说声就把快递放箱子 垃圾信息又多自动发送的信息没看见 过了几天问卖家才知道早到了 一天一元的存放费 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114275}, {"id": 273438, "content": "相互理解吧，各有各的不便之处。\n主要送我们家那片区的快递小哥都搞熟悉了。当然，不打不相识?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220178}, {"id": 273439, "content": "物流上显示已签收，过了三四天也没人说让我去取快递", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788971}, {"id": 273441, "content": "相信我，用菜鸟驿站是个好方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714055}, {"id": 273442, "content": "送快递，不发货。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290419}, {"id": 273446, "content": "放在别人小区的快递箱里，那个小区还很难进去，要门禁卡。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244033}, {"id": 273447, "content": "包装太大，把快递箱门卡坏了。打不开了。。。。哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244033}, {"id": 273448, "content": "快递柜太小就很尴尬了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299215}, {"id": 288808, "content": "等快递就是一件煎熬的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 273449, "content": "为什么都代收点？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？为什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282958}, {"id": 273450, "content": "把东西给我寄没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299291}, {"id": 273451, "content": "被快递员骚扰，一直被要求加微信，现在买个东西都提心吊胆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299294}, {"id": 273452, "content": "我来了，他走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 273453, "content": "为了凑运费买了好几个结果不同仓发货拆成好几个快递", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568528}, {"id": 273710, "content": "被水井签收", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300874}, {"id": 273455, "content": "代取费用有点小贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299316}, {"id": 273456, "content": "快递被放在邻居家狗旁边，我………没命拿", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290538}, {"id": 273460, "content": "把我的身份证和家乡特产弄丢了，强力抵制百世汇通", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295386}, {"id": 273461, "content": "快递员大声在门口大声喊你名字 以至于整栋楼都知道你叫什么。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299365}, {"id": 273718, "content": "你五点过来拿快递吧，结果我五点过去就关门了。??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296212}, {"id": 273464, "content": "不通知你直接放快递柜，超24小时没拿就给你取出退回，真是呵呵哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792424}, {"id": 273465, "content": "门口的快递就是不送上门，每次都打电话让你自己去取！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041395}, {"id": 273466, "content": "我买了一箱书发到办公室，结果快递用的是一个印满杜蕾斯logo的大箱子，并放在前台！面对各种异样眼光，一个并没有性生活的少女该如何解释．．．", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299475}, {"id": 273468, "content": "楼下那个说某猫超市买了5件分4个件的同学，你是买了一次买了多少卫生纸和洗衣液啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273908}, {"id": 273469, "content": "现在没有上门呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 273476, "content": "您的快递已放到门口消防拴，请回家自取", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116180}, {"id": 273739, "content": "快递不用看短信，直接拿，拿错那次麻烦我两天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885717}]}